And 'Circumscribed' radio button is enabled
And 'Non-circumscribed' radio button is enabled

And 'Oval' radio button is enabled
And 'Round' radio button is enabled
And 'Irregular' radio button is enabled

And 'T2w signal' is enabled

And 'Circumscribed fluid collection' checkbox is enabled
And 'Cystic-necrotic' checkbox is enabled
And 'Dilatation of seminal vesicular tubules' checkbox is enabled
And 'Perifocal edema' checkbox is enabled

And 'Strong' radio button is enabled
And 'Low' radio button is enabled
And 'No' radio button is enabled

And 'Diffusion restriction' checkbox is enabled

